[9.757391, "o", "# Compliance gap scan: wm-ops-agent\r\n\r\nJurisdiction: DE\r\nGenerated: 2026-06-26T00:19:46.677Z\r\n\r\n> This report is informational and is not legal advice. Every obligation it lists traces to a reference recorded in the rules data and validated by a maintainer. Confirm your obligations with qualified counsel.\r\n\r\n## Summary\r\n\r\n11 gap(s) found (high: 6, medium: 5).\r\n\r\n## National law (DE)\r\n\r\n### [high] Agent acts on an in-scope system with no risk analysis and information system security policies declared\r\n\r\n- Category: nis2-risk-management\r\n- Rule: nis2.risk-management.in-scope-no-a-riskanalysis\r\n- Triggered by: deployment:wm-ops-agent\r\n- Reference: NIS2 § 30 Abs. 2 Nr. 1 BSIG, DE BSIG (NIS2UmsuCG 2025)\r\n- Guidance: Declare policies for risk analysis and information system security.\r\n\r\n### [high] Agent acts on an in-scope system with no incident handling declared\r\n"]
